Package: riskdiff
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("John", "Murphy", , "jackmurphy2351@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The `riskdiff` package provides robust methods for calculating risk differences (also known as prevalence differences in cross-sectional studies) using generalized linear models. The package automatically selects appropriate link functions and provides publication-ready output.
